figure.sourcecode:
Lineage Execution A:
PCA1-A { BACKUP }

Lineage Execution B:
PCA0-B { WRITE-S3 }

Invalid successor of A:
{ BACKUP, WRITE-S3 }

WRITE-S3 did not originate in A.
The PCA is not a valid continuation of A.

